      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/myr-usd-malaysian-ringgit-gets-another-boost-from-foreign-bond-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚林吉特的上涨吸引全球基金购买更多本地债券，进一步提振本季度新兴市场表现最好的货币。]]></description>
